{"tid":2431972,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【I/A/Steam】Smash Legends｜跨平台 3 分鐘多人線上動作大亂鬥遊戲 !","createTime":"2021-03-04T04:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T08:53:29.000Z","uid":66923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"de582570a2fcc58736667255a36bb08764f219f4","tid":2431972,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bGVn3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bGVn3M.jpg&h=4bf06349&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《SMASH LEGEND‪S》是一款每場約 3 分鐘的線上動作對戰遊戲，玩家們將選擇自己喜歡的英雄進行 3 VS 3 的隊制團體戰，在浮島上的競技場擊倒敵人取得勝利，如果喜歡簡單操作節奏明快的動作遊戲，《SMASH LEGEND‪S》將會是最好選擇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=px7_yck21WY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpx7_yck21WY&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=f3366b21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=px7_yck21WY</a><br />\n除了 3 VS 3基本隊制死亡競賽模式外，還有 3 VS 3 的佔領模式、8 人大逃殺模式、4 人自由戰的水果收集模式、以及 1 VS 1 的戰挑模式等！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJZS9OA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJZS9OA.png&h=67b9fcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgyAn6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgyAn6F.jpg&h=c834814f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBYgRZ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBYgRZ0.jpg&h=f862efcd&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GfGiE0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GfGiE0.png&h=e97b6fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3S8kzds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3S8kzds.jpg&h=95a28c04&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2ctH6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2ctH6N.jpg&h=f4daa294&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqfvbZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqfvbZ7.jpg&h=cdcc282a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《SMASH LEGEND‪S》暫時率先於英國、挪威、芬蘭、瑞典、丹麥等歐洲國家上架，未來將會推展到全球國家地區推出，並會推出對應跨平台的 PC Steam 版。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ubNGXGdQDdo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DubNGXGdQDdo&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=b000b2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ubNGXGdQDdo</a><br />\n<br />\niOS : <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/fi/app/smash-legends/id1492660284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Ffi%2Fapp%2Fsmash-legends%2Fid1492660284&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=121e6ae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/fi/app/smash-legends/id1492660284</a><br />\nAndroid : <a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/16919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F16919&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=966d9527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/16919</a>"},{"pid":"c38932c2cebc9445c35bb1a5b3cd6c2c1546f2c8","tid":2431972,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"近排多翻依類game 彩虹冒險feel"},{"pid":"3590b4de43ad202e310501d9c859d6a07b261a16","tid":2431972,"uid":54090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"要轉去邊個國家app store  down?"},{"pid":"23465c418466263a2b84b3d29bd71be316cd5178","tid":2431972,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3590b4de43ad202e310501d9c859d6a07b261a16","tid":2431972,"uid":54090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"要轉去邊個國家app store  down?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"《SMASH LEGEND‪S》暫時率先於英國、挪威、芬蘭、瑞典